dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase "Taylor_PLSS_2018.gdb". [Coordinates of PLSS corners supplied by the Taylor County Surveyor. Data collected by direct observation using survey grade GPS. Coordinates entered manually by GIS Specialist to create GIS point file. PLSS section created and subdivided by GIS Specialist.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Used as the basis for all parcel mapping in Taylor County.]
